result:
<a-modal
  title="操作"
  :width="600"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
>
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">

      <a-form-item
        label="父级ID"
      >
        <a-input v-decorator="['parentId', {}]" disabled />
      </a-form-item>

      <a-form-item
        label="机构名称"
      >
        <a-input v-decorator="['orgName', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
